N and MERN stacks) and cross-platform mobile development (Flutter). By combining clean backend REST APIs with lightweight mobile and web frontends, we help startups and local brands establish highly reliable product ecosystems.\n                </p>\n              </AnimateOnScroll>\n            </div>\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      {/* Values */}\n      <section className=\"py-20 bg-bg-alt/20 border-t border-b border-border-main/50\">\n        <div className=\"container-max\">\n          <div className=\"max-w-2xl mb-16\">\n            <AnimateOnScroll>\n              <span className=\"text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-muted block mb-3\">\n                Our Values\n              </span>\n              <h2 className=\"font-heading text-3xl text-text-main\">\n                What We Stand For\n              </h2>\n            </AnimateOnScroll>\n          </div>\n\n          <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8\">\n            {values.map((v, index) => (\n              <AnimateOnScroll key={v.title} delay={index * 0.15}>\n                <div className=\"bg-surface border border-border-main rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-sm hover:shadow-md transition-shadow duration-300\">\n                  <div className=\"text-cta text-2xl font-bold mb-4\">{v.icon}</div>\n                  <h4 className=\"font-heading text-lg font-semibold text-text-main mb-3\">\n                    {v.title}\n                  </h4>\n                  <p className=\"text-muted text-sm leading-relaxed\">{v.desc}</p>\n                </div>\n              </AnimateOnScroll>\n            ))}\n          </div>\n        </div>\n      </section>\n\n      {/* Capabilities */}\n      <section className=\"py-20 bg-surface\">\n        <div className=\"container-max\">\n          <div className=\"max-w-2xl mb-16\">\n            <AnimateOnScroll>\n              <span className=\"text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-muted block mb-3\">\n    